{"tid":1296483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一切都係習鄭搞出嚟 唔好再 牽涉林先生好無？","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:11:44.000Z","uid":51717,"like":20,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a901f526dd4fd4dd31cc841b81e43548fd1264","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"林先生只係錯在娶咗個柒婆，同埋無同個柒婆離婚。諗深一層，柒婆唔同林生結婚，以佢個仆街性格，一樣會搞死香港，所以屌個柒婆時，下下拉埋佢夫家個姓嘅屌，對林生係好唔公平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，柒婆根本一個人唔敢做咁大決定，一定係習帝授權。示威抗議唔針對，就係無對正焦點。到而家啲人仲驚住話唔好激嬲共產黨，避談習大大，連提下佢個名都唔敢，佢係&ldquo;佛地魔&rdquo;？根本係佢兩人共同作惡先搞唔到香港咁。<br />\n<br />\n以後要屌，唔該習鄭一齊屌，唔好牽涉林生。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">習鄭下台！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"08b2d3dd399e57a3ee14a4411ab7d6e37177a93a","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0bff0bc3db32d1c8b6576a423eb75c0bd56dec3","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dd03d3448f0f8321a8f2b9ed820f4a03f64be35","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"你屌柒婆，佢可以推卸晒畀中央，習帝又可以話係香港自己決定。<br />\n<br />\n習鄭根本就二為一體，但又互扯貓尾又扮互推責任，一定要將佢兩個綑綁一齊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求習鄭出嚟回應市民</span></span>"},{"pid":"5fe8ecb3a763be78e2682442d9020e46179a38ba","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf1a230d5f7d1cd2473fb4d233a8324a66ccc0c8","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee5e6a10bc24a2555b2b93f10d715237fcc1a5cc","tid":1296483,"uid":119572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"習鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d34b703e9d362dfeec297a94cc725376e608fa5","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee5e6a10bc24a2555b2b93f10d715237fcc1a5cc","tid":1296483,"uid":119572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"習鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"遊行示威如果大大塊牌咁寫<br />\n<br />\n一定上晒頭頭，國際報紙都咁影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20eaf970a2ce57da155465fd2802e89c63531a2","tid":1296483,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"以後好唔好叫佢習鄭月娥"},{"pid":"019d48310b9a1943980f9c2e730d50b8f7b2df90","tid":1296483,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"林奠食習腸，含到習腸閃令令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6799047625f5471c23a344f2e075adfe09e87fac","tid":1296483,"uid":114537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dfa46da9979dafaf762c7d09d0d4b370749747","tid":1296483,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"019d48310b9a1943980f9c2e730d50b8f7b2df90","tid":1296483,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"林奠食習腸，含到習腸閃令令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\